{"id":37497,"type":4,"name":"Galaxy on Fire 2","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/b9/27/37497_gIeij.jpg","rating":{"total":51,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":1,"4":1,"5":2,"6":3,"7":11,"8":18,"9":8,"10":7},"score":7.8},"summary":"　　浴火银河2(galaxy on fire 2)是一款具有角色扮演色彩的3D飞行射击类游戏,是继前作浴火银河的第二作,由德国顶尖手机3D游戏开发商Fishlabs研制,并采用了其独有的开发引擎ABYSS,在手机3D游戏中处于技术绝对领先的地位,效果甚至能够赶上PlayStation.在浩瀚的银河中,玩家可以在数十个空间站点之间遨游,执行多样化的艰巨任务,并且可以购买更先进的飞行器进行作战。\r\n　　相比前作，二代增加了采矿系统，牵引光束系统，僚机系统，舰炮系统，导弹系统，EMP能量系统，星门跃迁系统，隐形系统，货仓压缩系统和客舱系统等亮点，任务也做了大幅革新，更加有趣味性和挑战性，此外，在前作基础上，新增了十几种全新的飞船，画面也变得更为精细，给予玩家完美的游戏体验。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>浴火银河2</li><li><span>别名: </span>GOF2</li><li><span>平台: </span>PC</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>iOS</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>Zeebo</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>Symbian</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>MeeGo</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>Java</li><li><span>游戏类型: </span>Space flight simulator game</li><li><span>游戏引擎: </span>ABYSS</li><li><span>游玩人数: </span>1人</li><li><span>发行日期: </span>2009年2月 2012年8月21日(PC)</li><li><span>官方网站: </span>http://www.galaxyonfire.com/</li>","collection":{"wish":4,"collect":52,"doing":1,"dropped":5},"tags":[{"name":"科幻","count":10},{"name":"IOS","count":10},{"name":"星辰大海","count":4},{"name":"太空","count":4},{"name":"手游","count":3},{"name":"PC","count":3},{"name":"开放世界","count":2},{"name":"2009","count":2},{"name":"STG","count":2},{"name":"Fishlabs","count":1}],"like":[{"id":26449,"name":"人类衰退之后","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/41/39/26449_G0Xzx.jpg"},{"id":927,"name":"秒速5厘米","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/1f/44/927_J2Q9a.jpg"},{"id":2227,"name":"osu!","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/ef/df/2227_870yo.jpg"},{"id":485,"name":"凉宫春日的忧郁","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/21/8a/485_Et062.jpg"},{"id":24790,"name":"男子高中生的日常","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/c5/73/24790_4wdXB.jpg"},{"id":23686,"name":"刀剑神域","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/co